{
  "texts": [
    "This analysis forms the basis for generating recommendations.",
    "• Recommendation Generation: Based on the identified patterns, the system predicts how a user would rate items they have not yet interacted with.",
    "These predictions are used to generate a personalized list of product recommendations.",
    "• Feedback Mechanism: User interactions with the recommended products (such as clicks, views, and purchases) are tracked.",
    "This feedback is used to continuously refine the recommendation algorithm."
  ]
}